    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A very narrow stipe repeated at intervals, usually present in woven or printed cloth, but also used to describe such a stripe in paintings or other works.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
